<h1>This is your friend {{foundFriend.friendName}} profile page!</h1>

<h3> Full name: {{foundFriend.friendName}} {{foundFriend.friendSurname}} </h3>
<h3> City: {{foundFriend.city}}</h3>
<h3> Birthday: {{foundFriend.birthday}}</h3>
<img style="width: 150px" src="{{foundFriend.avatar}}" alt="avatar picture">
